flowchart TB
    subgraph Sources
        TERMINAL[Terminal<br>zsh hooks]
        CLAUDE_CODE[Claude Code<br>session files]
    end

    subgraph Storage ["~/.ambient/"]
        EVENTS_LOG[logs/<br>events-YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl]
        ANALYSIS_LOG[analysis/<br>analysis-YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl]
        SUMMARY_MD[analysis/<br>summary-YYYY-MM-DD.md]
        WEEKLY_MD[analysis/<br>weekly-YYYY-MM-DD.md]
        INSIGHTS_MD[insights/<br>insights-YYYY-MM-DD.md]
        RECS_DIR[recommendations/<br>*.md]
        GMM_MODEL[models/<br>gmm.joblib]
        STATE[daemon/<br>state.json]
    end

    subgraph API
        HAIKU[Claude Haiku<br>batch + skills]
        SONNET[Claude Sonnet<br>daily + weekly + insights]
    end

    TERMINAL -->|preexec/precmd<br>append JSONL| EVENTS_LOG
    CLAUDE_CODE -->|session_parser<br>incremental| EVENTS_LOG

    EVENTS_LOG -->|detectors| ANALYSIS_LOG
    ANALYSIS_LOG -->|build_batch_prompt| HAIKU
    HAIKU -->|JSON findings| ANALYSIS_LOG

    ANALYSIS_LOG -->|build_daily_prompt| SONNET
    SONNET -->|narrative| SUMMARY_MD

    ANALYSIS_LOG -->|build_weekly_prompt<br>+ coaching data| SONNET
    SONNET -->|trend report| WEEKLY_MD

    EVENTS_LOG -->|aggregate_coaching_data| SONNET
    SONNET -->|coaching report| INSIGHTS_MD

    EVENTS_LOG -->|prompt patterns<br>+ stuck patterns| HAIKU
    HAIKU -->|skill/rule drafts| RECS_DIR

    EVENTS_LOG -->|pause gaps| GMM_MODEL
    GMM_MODEL -->|classifications| ANALYSIS_LOG

    STATE -->|cursors + processed sessions| EVENTS_LOG

    style Sources fill:#003049,stroke:#d62828,color:#fff
    style Storage fill:#1d3557,stroke:#457b9d,color:#fff
    style API fill:#6a040f,stroke:#e85d04,color:#fff
